The door to the tower opened and out stepped Lord Perseus, followed by
Kenzo.

&quot;Ok Maximals.  Our base it totally destroyed, and we&#39;ve done all we can for
these people.&quot; Lord Perseus said, with a touch of sadness in his voice.  &quot;We
are packed up and ready to move, my plan is to return to our Maximal
brethren and perhaps work out some sort of cooperation agreement.  I fear if
we remain here, we will only bring more suffering to these people.&quot;

As he walked across the bridge toward the group, he noticed a strange face.

&quot;You there!&quot; he said, addressing Tuscon. &quot;Do you intend to join us?&quot;

