&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt;
&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &quot;Yes. I&#39;ve come to the conclusion that our presence in the city
&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; merely aggrivates conditions. Without us, this island would become a
&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; much lower priority for our enemies. Though I hope we can continue
&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; our research together; and I promise we will do anything we can to
&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; help the city.&quot;
&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt;
&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &quot;So where will you be going?&quot; the mayor asked after a moment of
&gt; silence.
&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt;
&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Perseus walked to the windows and sighed.
&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt;
&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &quot;We Maximals have been divided for too long. With this Unicronian
&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; threat, and our recent truce with Megatron. it would be apropriate
&gt; for
&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; us to put our diferences aside and work together. So we&#39;ll first be
&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; going to meet with Lord Elder.&quot;
&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt;
&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &quot;Well my friend, I wish you the best of success. You are always
&gt; welcome
&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; here.&quot;
&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt;
&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &quot;Thank you.&quot;
